tps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZdFSXg.png&h=05609ed4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"嚇我唔到嘅 ，係技術性調整<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732fbe6bb691eae91463eb4a1b193fa2c33172a2","tid":1038304,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"依加買10蚊<br />\n到時移民火星就靠佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ff8de706cbfe8c3c804432e960382048fd1556","tid":1038304,"uid":13640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"[睇圖避莊家股濕9 FCC幣]<br />\n股權過度集中嘅產品容易俾莊家舞高弄低, 因此除你好熟莊家心, 否則因此睇圖玩係冇用, 因為大戶曉畫圖。<br />\n斃少嘅FCC貨源一樣歸哂邊, 同一啲莊家股走勢亦相似，一齊睇睇。<br />\n***首先要知莊家貨底成本非常低。老散唔好以為股跌個莊會蝕錢。咩價套現佢都贏。10蚊跌到1蚊以為好抵。但忽略咗垃圾其實1毫都唔值。***<br />\nStage 1: 大戶放風隻嘢好有前途, 左手交右手托。散戶貪新鮮。大升<br />\nStage 2: 高位難吸引更多散戶入市, 大戶震倉等老散以為有靚位入。<br />\nStage 3: 再次左手交右手搭棚。<br />\nStage 4: 大陰燭。大戶要錢唔要貨。質低個價, 等散戶以為好抵狗衝接, 成交量升。<br />\nStage 5: 陽燭後抽。沽壓暫減, 散戶血肉長城。散戶以為調整完畢追入。<br />\nStage 6: repeat stage 4, 成交量增係因為散戶繼續唔識死接貨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48392207_2072396282825723_5356322013411540992_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=284f506dcdca5d41a79d1a59a515ea02&amp;oe=5D200A7B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F48392207_2072396282825723_5356322013411540992_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D284f506dcdca5d41a79d1a59a515ea02%26oe%3D5D200A7B&h=e1d99b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48404979_2072396309492387_1387538809024937984_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=64eb2cc71625ef864968f78074215ff7&amp;oe=5CDA5581\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F484049